{"tha-ap119:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap119:0.2":"Mahaparivaravagga ","tha-ap119:0.3":"Buddhasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap119:1.1":"“Yada vipassi lokaggo, ","tha-ap119:1.2":"ayusankharamossaji; ","tha-ap119:1.3":"Pathavi sampakampittha, ","tha-ap119:1.4":"medani jalamekhala. ","tha-ap119:2.1":"Otatam vitthatam mayham, ","tha-ap119:2.2":"suvicittavatamsakam; ","tha-ap119:2.3":"Bhavanampi pakampittha, ","tha-ap119:2.4":"buddhassa ayusankhaye. ","tha-ap119:3.1":"Taso mayham samuppanno, ","tha-ap119:3.2":"bhavane sampakampite; ","tha-ap119:3.3":"Uppado nu kimatthaya, ","tha-ap119:3.4":"aloko vipulo ahu. ","tha-ap119:4.1":"Vessavano idhagamma, ","tha-ap119:4.2":"nibbapesi mahajanam; ","tha-ap119:4.3":"Panabhute bhayam natthi, ","tha-ap119:4.4":"ekagga hotha samvuta. ","tha-ap119:5.1":"Aho buddha aho dhamma, ","tha-ap119:5.2":"aho no satthu sampada; ","tha-ap119:5.3":"Yasmim uppajjamanamhi, ","tha-ap119:5.4":"pathavi sampakampati. ","tha-ap119:6.1":"Buddhanubhavam kittetva, ","tha-ap119:6.2":"kappam saggamhi modaham; ","tha-ap119:6.3":"Avasesesu kappesu, ","tha-ap119:6.4":"kusalam caritam maya. ","tha-ap119:7.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap119:7.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap119:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap119:7.4":"buddhasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap119:8.1":"Ito cuddasakappamhi, ","tha-ap119:8.2":"raja asim patapava; ","tha-ap119:8.3":"Samito nama namena, ","tha-ap119:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap119:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap119:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap119:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap119:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma buddhasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap119:11.1":"Buddhasannakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}